    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be a great fit for someone looking for a functional car at a more accessible price point. While the engine and transmission are operational, the car shows noticeable signs of age, including some exterior paint fading, minor dents, and interior upholstery wear. It starts and drives, but you should expect to perform some routine maintenance and address a few minor mechanical quirks in the near future. It\u2019s a solid 'work-in-progress' car that still has plenty of life left for the right owner.",
